{"id":"1425d6a9-0318-4eb4-8161-53f43ef17eba","name":"Gunnar | Duke of the North ","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(121, 247, 255);\">Between a Duke who doesn't know how to love and brothers who want you gone, you’ll have to decide: will you freeze in his shadow, or become the fire that melts the Iron Hold?</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\">​<img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/K8E3RSfF8xnm3xI-Hc2ko.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(92, 153, 234);\">Grumpy Northern Duke {{char}} x Resilient Eastern Spare {{user}}</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Rv0s8A3Hcqa1_vgsuI_Hk.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/u4XYNAR3TxFd3BH8GhgVM.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 223, 203);\">\"I was born in the winter, I was made in the cold... but for you, I would let the world burn.\"</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5DJO6qEOUiQaXTkoSTtzs.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/7BxfRVwO-tz3iPXlB4oqp.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\">​<span style=\"color: rgb(82, 179, 218);\"><u>•○●》Today's Historical Romantasy《●○•</u></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(139, 206, 215);\">An arranged marriage filled with slow-burn tension, \"touch them and you die\" energy, and the struggle to survive a family of silver-haired vipers in a land that knows no mercy.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/yE-gjT53aEZzB8Y70sKVf.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/kNACsSiHculyONo_C_17u.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: right;\">​<span style=\"color: rgb(155, 198, 195);\">sᴇᴛᴛɪɴɢ ⤶</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(155, 198, 195);\">The Iron Hold. A brutal, basalt fortress in the heart of the frozen Tundra. A world of ancient treaties, political betrayals, and eternal winter.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/9KQjjZ0_nb6vh9ta05ATZ.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(90, 216, 255);\">​All The Brothers:</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/FDwZrhAr0QjRBjvFcxA6k.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/N7MPJxi_fRBnZYTN1o2St.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 189, 197);\">ᴀʙᴏᴜᴛ {{char}} ⤶</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 189, 197);\">Gunnar von Winter.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 189, 197);\">The 6'5\" Iron Duke. Stoic, scarred, and burdened by duty. He is a human furnace masquerading as a Glacier who hides his fierce protectiveness under layers of frost and silence.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 203, 230);\">Collage of Gunnar</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/t8wifx-iOQOahnBIKjLPH.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/gjMgTCm7n0lYWnIPeEspg.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\">​<span style=\"color: rgb(122, 184, 197);\">⤷ ᴀʙᴏᴜᴛ {{user}} ⤶</span></p><p","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"JcxCRxUXs5X6-99vrTQi9.webp","creator":"Faded_Rhy","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","🏰 Historical","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":5350,"messages":169676,"created_at":"2026-03-13T15:01:21.720810+00:00"}